<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('./partials/head') %>
        <title>About - Blogify</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
    <%- include('./partials/navbar') %>

        <main class="container my-5">
            <section class="mb-5 text-center">
                <h1 class="mb-3">About <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="img-fluid m-2" style="height: 50px;"><span class="text-primary">Blogify</span></h1>
                <p class="lead text-muted">
                    Blogify is a modern, full-featured blogging platform designed for seamless content creation and
                    interaction. It empowers users with a personalized space to express ideas, share knowledge, and
                    engage in meaningful discussions.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="row text-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-rss fa-3x mb-2 text-warning"></i> <!-- Changed from text-primary -->
                    <h5>Explore Blogs</h5>
                    <p>View the latest blogs, trending posts, and explore content by popular authors.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus fa-3x mb-2 text-teal" style="color: #20c997;"></i> <!-- Custom teal color -->
                    <h5>User Features</h5>
                    <p>Sign up, login, and manage your account. Create, edit, or delete blogs and comments easily.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-shield fa-3x mb-2 text-violet" style="color: #6f42c1;"></i> <!-- Custom violet color -->
                    <h5>Admin Control</h5>
                    <p>Admins can manage all users, blogs, and comments with a powerful dashboard for moderation.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-5">
                <h4>Key Features</h4>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-eye text-success me-2"></i> View detailed blogs and
                        author profiles</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-comments text-info me-2"></i> Comment on blogs
                        (highlighted author comments)</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-pencil-alt text-warning me-2"></i> Edit and delete only
                        your own content</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-user-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Account panel to
                        manage your blogs and comments</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-user-times text-danger me-2"></i> Deleting users also
                        removes their blogs & comments</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-cogs text-secondary me-2"></i> Role-based access:
                        viewer, author, admin, admin-author</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-search text-dark me-2"></i> Powerful search using
                        MongoDB text indexing</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-image text-success me-2"></i> Profile and cover image
                        uploads for enhanced UI</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-5">
                <h4>Tech Stack</h4>
                <div class="row text-center">
                    <div class="col-md-3"><i class="fab fa-html5 fa-2x text-danger"></i>
                        <p>HTML</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3"><i class="fab fa-css3-alt fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <p>CSS</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3"><i class="fab fa-js-square fa-2x text-warning"></i>
                        <p>JavaScript</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3"><i class="fab fa-node fa-2x text-success"></i>
                        <p>Node.js</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3"><i class="fas fa-database fa-2x text-dark"></i>
                        <p>MongoDB</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt fa-2x text-secondary"></i>
                        <p>JWT Auth</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3"><i class="fas fa-key fa-2x text-info"></i>
                        <p>Password Hashing</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3"><i class="fas fa-tools fa-2x text-muted"></i>
                        <p>Express.js</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="border-top pt-4">
                <h4 class="text-center mb-4">About Me</h4>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                    <img src="/images/profileJatin.png" alt="Profile Image" class="rounded-circle mb-3" width="120"
                        height="120">
                    <h5>Jatin Carpenter</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted">CSE Student at IET DAVV</p>
                    <p class="text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap text-primary me-2"></i> Aspiring Full Stack Web Developer
                        specializing in the <strong>MERN Stack</strong> (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js).<br>
                        <i class="fas fa-laptop-code text-success me-2"></i> Currently diving deep into <strong>web
                            technologies</strong> and modern JavaScript frameworks.<br>
                        <i class="fas fa-code text-warning me-2"></i> Enthusiast of <strong>competitive
                            programming</strong> and core computer science concepts.<br>
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket text-danger me-2"></i> Passionate about building dynamic, scalable, and
                        responsive web applications.<br>
                        <i class="fas fa-bullseye text-info me-2"></i> Focused on pursuing a professional career as a
                        <strong>Full Stack Web Developer</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3 mt-2">
                        <a href="https://github.com/JatinCarpenter07" target="_blank"><i
                                class="fab fa-github fa-lg text-dark"></i></a>
                        <a href="https://in.linkedin.com/in/jatin-carpenter-b769a0260" target="_blank"><i
                                class="fab fa-linkedin fa-lg text-dark"></i></a>
                        <a href="mailto:jatincarpentar64@gmail.com"><i class="fas fa-envelope fa-lg text-dark"></i></a>
                        <a href="tel:+916264387622"><i class="fas fa-phone fa-lg text-dark"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
            <%- include('./partials/script') %>
</body>

</html>